api_list.name: LastDraw
api_list.description: Returns the last draw result, with or without the prize table
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://limestudio-thailottery.p.rapidapi.com/v1/Results/ThaiLotto/LastDraw"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "limestudio-thailottery.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
